high_descs: Walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the sink, after that turn right and walk forward.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the white box in front of you.
Turn left to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the sink then turn on the water, after a couple second turn off the water and remove the clean bar of soap.
Put the clean bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Take six steps forward then turn left for six steps, turn right and stop.
Pick up the pink soap from the white counter top.
Turn left to face the sink.
Place the soap vertically in the sink, to the left of the drain, turn on the water to fill the sink halfway, turn off the water and drain, pick up the soap.
Turn around and take three steps, turn right for seven steps, turn right to face the bathtub.
Place the soap in the tub, near the front and about halfway between the far right green item and the end of the tub, on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a bar of pink soap in the bathtub

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the soap below the towel.
Pick up the soap next to the tissues.
Turn left and look at the sink.
Rinse the soap in the sink and then pick up the soap from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the middle of the tub.
Place the soap in the middle of the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap in the tub.
